          </div>
          <div class="media">
            <a href="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/lockitron-unit.png"><img src="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/lockitron-unit.png" width="250" alt="Lockitron"/></a></div>
          <div class="media">
            <a href="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/iphone-app.png"><img src="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/iphone-app.png" width="250" alt="Lockitron iPhone Lock"/></a></div>
          <div class="media">
            <a href="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/iphone-users.png"><img src="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/iphone-users.png" width="250" alt="Lockitron iPhone Users"/></a>
          </div>
          <div class="media">
            <a href="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/android-app.png"><img src="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/android-app.png" width="250" alt="Lockitron Android App"/></a></div>
          <div class="media" style="padding-top: 75px; height: 92px"><a href="http://lockitron.com/press-kit/press-kit-2012.zip">Download the press pack</a>
          </div>
          <div style="clear:both">

